  author   = "Ainsworth, Elizabeth A and Gillespie, Kelly M",
  abstract = "Non-structural phenolic compounds perform a variety of functions
              in plants, including acting as antioxidants. We describe a
              microplate-adapted colorimetric total phenolics assay that
              utilizes Folin-Ciocalteu (F-C) reagent. The F-C assay relies on
