              electron transfer reaction is not specific for phenolic
              compounds, the extraction procedure eliminates approximately 85\%
              of ascorbic acid and other potentially interfering compounds.
              This assay is performed in microcentrifuge tubes and assessed in
              a 96-well plate reader. At least 64 samples can be processed in 1
              d.",
